Main Screen Key-commands:

 Cursor Up	Move Selector Bar up
 Cursor Down	Move Selector Bar down

	Enter	Play selected File or PlayList

	PgUp	Move one Page to the Top
	PgDn	Move one Page to the Bottom
	Home	Move to the Top
	End	Move to the Bottom
	Ins	Toggle Select File under Cursor
	Del	Unselect File under Cursor

KeyPad<+>	Select multiple Files
KeyPad<->	UnSelect multiple Files
KeyPad<*>	Reverse Selection
KeyPad</>	Select known Filetypes
	
	F1	Generic Help
	F2	Stop Playing
	F3	
	F4	Edit PlayListFile (wenn keine playList, dann nochmal nachfragenm, ob wirklich editiert werden soll)
	F5	Copy selected Files
	F6	Rename selected Files
	F7	Search for a File
	F8	Delete selected Files
	F9	Go to the Cntrol Menu
	F10	Exit Player

<Shift>+F1	Help on Hotkeys (this Screen)
<Shift>+F2	Add Files to PlayList
<Shift>+F3	See contents of PlayListFile
<Shift>+F4	
<Shift>+F5	Create new Playlist (durchsucht die platte!)
<Shift>+F6	Verify selected PlayList
<Shift>+F7	Find PlayListfiles
<Shift>+F8	Delete selected from PlayList
<Shift>+F9	
<Shift>+F10	Go to OS-Shell

 <Crtl>+F1	Left Window toggle (Fileselector,PlayList,...,Console)
 <Crtl>+F2	Right Window toggle (FileInfoScr,PlayInfoScr,InstrScr,...,Console)
 <Crtl>+F3	Sort Files by Name
 <Crtl>+F4	Sort Files by Type
 <Crtl>+F5	Sort Files by Time
 <Crtl>+F6	Sort Files by Size
 <Crtl>+F7	Do not sort Files
 <Crtl>+F8	Sort Files by Permissions (not in DOS)
 <Crtl>+F9
 <Crtl>+F10	Console Toggle (Backgr,Blobs,TextFFT,WasWeisIchWasMode,FullScr)


 <Ctrl>+L	Toggle long filenames
 <Ctrl>+R	Reload Directory
 <Ctrl>+PgUp	Move one Directory up
 <Ctrl>+PgDn	Move to Directory under Cursor (if File, don't Play)
 <Ctrl>+BkSpc	Move to RootDirectory

 <Ctrl>+O	Toggle Console to foreground
 <Ctrl>+M	Toggle Screen Meters
 <Ctrl>+B	Toggle Status-Bar on top

 <Ctrl>+W	Start DiskWriter with selected File
 <Ctrl>+S	Toggle Surround
 <Ctrl>+I	Toggle Interpolation
 <Ctrl>+F	Toggle Filters
